To compile eBook-speaker, be sure the following extra packages are installed:

   libncurses5-dev
   libncursesw5-dev
   libsox-dev
   libmagic-dev
   libxml2-dev
   libidn11-dev

Give the following command:

   $ make

Give, as user root, the following command to install eBook-speaker
onto your system:

   # make install
